    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice </strong>and <strong>cauliflower rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with 110ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [175ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[225ml]</span> cold water and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chinese-style-beef-and-green-pepper-stir-fry-with-cauliflower-rice/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, peel and roughly dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and dice</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chinese-style-beef-and-green-pepper-stir-fry-with-cauliflower-rice/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and cook for 3-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chinese-style-beef-and-green-pepper-stir-fry-with-cauliflower-rice/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chinese-style-beef-and-green-pepper-stir-fry-with-cauliflower-rice/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, increase the heat to high, then add your <strong>mince</strong> to the pan and cook over a high heat for 5 min or until browned all over, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>While the mince is browning, add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>black pepper</strong> to the pan (freshly ground is best!)</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chinese-style-beef-and-green-pepper-stir-fry-with-cauliflower-rice/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the mince has browned, add the <strong>diced pepper</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>ginger</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min further</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium-high and add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame oil</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until thickened and sticky and the mince is cooked through (no pink meat!) \u2013 this is your<strong> Chinese-style mince & green pepper stir-fry</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chinese-style-beef-and-green-pepper-stir-fry-with-cauliflower-rice/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Finely slice your <strong>red chilli[es]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>into rounds</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chinese-style-beef-and-green-pepper-stir-fry-with-cauliflower-rice/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Chinese-style mince & green pepper stir-fry</strong> over the <strong>cooked cauliflower rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> chilli rounds </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
